Gina DeVettori https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gina_DeVettori 0 Gina DeVettori (born May 5 in California) is an American actress and writer. DeVettori was born on Cinco de Mayo and is a native Californian. She graduated from the University of Mobile with a Bachelor of Arts in theatre.
